Capture `run_id` before the param-logging loop and ensure cleanup on failure:
```python
run_id = str(run.info.run_id)
try:
    for k, v in dict(params).items():
        client.log_param(run_id, k, v)
except Exception:
    try:
        client.set_terminated(run_id, status='FAILED')
    except Exception:
        pass
    raise
```
